    "summary": "Work with entertainment industry always was my dream and be part of this universe for 18 years is amazing!\n\nMy career started as a journalist for tech and gaming markets (I have more than 1000 published articles in more than 40 media outlets). The experience as media drive me to start my first digital agency, an startup formed by an high talent millennial team which I'm very proud to have leaded. Together we had brought to life outstanding projects for global companies for B2B market.\n\nLooking for new challenges and curious to live the Marketing for B2C I accepted the mission to be part of the marketing team of the biggest Brazilian computer manufacture and changed my mind-set to think in solutions and strategies to consumer goods. \n\nI'm fulfilled professional to have been worked and learned about the 3 pillars of market (media, agency and client). This knowledge lined up with my passion for art and games lead me to create the project Game Concept Art Brasil, the first online free platform with the mission to bring knowledge and resources for anyone who dreams to be an artist in the gaming industry.\n\nAfter almost 2 decades absorbing all experience which the Brazilian market have to teach, I've came to Europe seeking for new challenges with a backpack full of ideas and desire do grow more as a professional. \n\nAs we all gamers know: It's dangerous to go alone. So take me and let's create our future together!\n\nSpecialities:\nGlobal Game Industry, Project Management, Brand Marketing, Inbound Marketing Strategies, Team leadership, Packaging, Concept Art, Digital Design.",
